race.comment: SKYTALKER (4) jumped favourite here last start and just missed in a photo finish. Out to 1500m again now for just the second time, but he maps well and the rise in trip doesn't look an issue. Can go one better this time around. FIGHT IN FLIGHT (9) couldn't bring up the hat-trick last start when tackling Saturday grade at Ascot. Her two wins here prior were strong and put in good ratings. Back to the scene of the crime now and she can return to winning ways. FLYING SOUTH (3) jumped favourite over this track and trip last start and never really got into the race. Nottle's claim comes in handy today and he can return to his best form. IMPOSING BROOK (5) got the job done narrowly here 25 days ago and has the speed to work across from the deep. Can be in this for a long way. THE SPRUIKER (1) will find this easier than his past couple of outings and is not to be discounted.
